衰<br />\n有諗過一次過講清楚 但我驚以後連朋友都冇得做<br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以俾下意見我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不如講下佢有咩咁吸引你?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可能因為自己一個住嘅關係 相處耐左就好依賴佢<br />\n習慣左有佢 <br />\n試過令到自己好忙 以為忙就冇時間諗佢<br />\n但佢始終出現係我腦海 搭車諗 訓教前又諗"},{"pid":"4af5ca113de12253dab220004a7ed8387284e7f9","tid":94684,"uid":65750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:21:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自己有冇拍拖?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇 出現過唔少合適 比佢好嘅人<br />\n但始終放唔低佢 就冇拍"},{"pid":"05492616fe22965f46b3f962aacef507fba1cb29","tid":94684,"uid":5200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"你幾多歲 仲成個傻仔咁等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8522615929bf13e6a8c9872932820873f2e24019","tid":94684,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:28:31.000Z","msg":"頭搖又尾擺 SKY !"},{"pid":"c0e6fb60916b99a7e68e48a5e3bfbe288d0b6a9b","tid":94684,"uid":65750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:34:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你幾多歲 仲成個傻仔咁等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十六等到二十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊啲朋友都係咁講 叫我放棄 但我唔想"},{"pid":"7089104386ca78505ccfeb232041a44c14911cc3","tid":94684,"uid":5200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你幾多歲 仲成個傻仔咁等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十六等到二十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊啲朋友都係咁講 叫我放棄 但我唔想</blockquote><br />\n你廿歲就一個人住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}