:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"佢有冇食到你？<br />\n冇嘅話真係唔知叫好彩定唔彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有食 - 咩都蝕哂俾佢 佢仍然當你一舊屎<br />\n冇食 - 你連食用價值都冇"},{"pid":"be5cfe00dae526e113be5ad16c185ff326406ad8","tid":94684,"uid":660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:12:54.000Z","msg":"你不如主動d 佢唔肯同你進一步發展咪死心"},{"pid":"d9416bc93e1a7758fb56e60461fc122a10788f68","tid":94684,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:17:14.000Z","msg":"你呢d 人真係麻煩<br />\n咩因為一個人住而倚賴人<br />\n呢d根本唔係戀愛原因<br />\n只係因爲佢就手夠方便<br />\n你係咪條件好差所以做到咁"},{"pid":"3ecc0283153adf65a8bb194dd7cbb2062e9762b8","tid":94684,"uid":6091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:20:00.000Z","msg":"種咩因得咩果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}